      "date": "2013-02-21 14:36:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/009b3d7e-7c34-11e2-897d-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
