          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-02-21 20:17:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/68e1bf2a-7c61-11e2-897d-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
